snippet.title: Jetborne Racing - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1397650/Jetborne_Racing
Jetborne Racing is an online multiplayer air racing game from the creator of VTOL VR. Pilot a high performance jet aircraft through challenging courses in a race to the finish. Fly in VR (recommended) or on desktop with either virtual or physical HOTAS controls. Compete in up to 8-player online races or run hot laps to rank in global lap-time leaderboards. Get immersed in the heart-pounding sensation of flying over Mach 1 through tight and and technical race courses. Do you have what it takes for a podium position?
